---
---
REQUEST_URI=/book?foo=bar
REQUEST_METHOD=GET
SERVER_PROTOCOL=HTTP/1.1
---
---
Status: 200 OK
Content-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<meta charset="utf-8">
